{"title":"原来他是大粮商","authors":["张响涛"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来他是大粮商"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张响涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"富裕中农李吉祥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱烟袋儿尺半长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眯上眼睛抽一袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚里生出坏主张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统购统销他不满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大街小巷喊缺粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发财心儿总不死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像得了发财狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天三次找干部，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦眼抹泪装哭相："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我家早上没揭锅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枕头被子全吃光。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农村开始大鸣放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吉祥把戏露真相，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众纷纷来检举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来他是大粮商。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1957.9．唐山"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}